DESCRIPTION: Snekproof cards aren't affected by #yConfusion and cannot be #yMuddled.
Suits refer to card's color. Token cards do not count as Suits.
Overflow effects activate if you have more than 5 cards in hand.
Muddling a card changes its cost this turn to between #b0 and #b3 at random.
An Offclass card is any obtainable card from a class other than your own (including Colorless cards, Curses, and Statuses).
When you obtain this card, get a card reward with the following card type.
Replace an #yUnidentified card with its current random card permanently.
Creatures with Venom lose additional HP at the start of their turn if they have at least two additional debuffs.
#Overflow effects always activate this turn regardless of hand size.
